      "tex_block": "\\begin{claimmark}\n\\begin{Rem}\n    If $G$ is acyclic then also $G_{\\doit(W)}$ is acyclic and a topological order for $G$ is also one for $G_{\\doit(W)}$.\n\\end{Rem}\n\\end{claimmark}",
